Description: The ClothierShell package is a logical framework designed to calculate optimal clothing layering 
    strategies (shells) based on real-time meteorological data. By automating 
    thermal homeostasis decisions, this tool reduces decision fatigue for field 
    personnel, ensuring biological stability and uninterrupted workflow through 
    the application of a structured wardrobe logic engine.
